Satkalatra Yoga

At some point in life danger comes to the younger siblings, or those whom you consider your brothers and sisters.

Your mother may contact some disease or may become immoral.  Your maternal uncle will be a prominent person.

Your mother may become a widow.

Diseases will have a hard time overwhelming you.

Your sibling may be a commander-in-chief (a high position in army, navy or air force) or may become a great physician.

You will have much wealth.

You may be a very rich person or you will have a large number of children.

Wealth will improve in the periods of Venus, whereas this will not be the case in the periods of Jupiter.
Arishta Bhanga
Because you have the strong natural  benefic Jupiter in either a trine or angle house,  cancellation of all evils is indicated in the chart. This means that, when bad things come in the life, they will also automatically dissipate in strength, and the outcome will not be so bad. You are protected by divine grace and past good Karma.

You will be fortunate in general. It may mean gain from religion, preachers, etc. But on a deeper level it indicates fortune due to surrender to God in this and/or previous lives.

The birth of children is highly likely, especially during Jupiter periods.

You may adopt the son of your cousin. 

You may have an adopted child, or may  look after the children of others.

Fame and power will be conferred in this period.

Mercury will give favorable results during his periods.

The Moon will give favorable results during his periods.

Enlightened, cheerful and artistic. Wealth, interest in politics, skill with crafts, interest in philosophical literature, good speaking and singing abilities and other good qualities in general.

Physical felicity somewhat stripped away by diseases, legal battles, jail, or some type of binding, unpleasant restriction. You meet with obstacles, debts, disease or enemies on your path, but have the forcefulness to surmount them. You do well in positions of service and in medical or military fields.

You become insatiable, talkative, intent on wandering, and subjected to grief on account of the opposite sex.

You may be quite a wealthy person with influence in high places. You try to live a righteous life and are able to give pleasure to many. Also, your father will most likely live a long life.

Your children may become very wealthy and fortunate. You will be very powerful, do well and will be a friend of highly paced people. You are intelligent and educated, and will have many people who listen to your advice.

Your son may be inimical towards your. Your uncle will be wealthy and renowned.
